'''固缩'''（又叫'''细胞致密变化'''，{{lang-en|Pyknosis}}）是[[细胞|细胞]]经历[[坏死|坏死]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Kumar V, Abbas A, Nelson F, Mitchell R. |title=Robbins Basic Pathology |work=Robbins Basic Pathology |edition= 8th |pages=6, 9–10 |year=2007 }}</ref>或[[细胞凋亡|凋亡]]<ref name="zamzami">{{cite journal |author=Kroemer G, Galluzzi L, Vandenabeele P, ''et al.'' |title=Classification of cell death: recommendations of the Nomenclature Committee on Cell Death 2009 |journal=Cell Death Differ. |volume=16 |issue=1 |pages=3–11 |pmid=18846107 |pmc=2744427 |doi=10.1038/cdd.2008.150 |date=January 2009}}</ref>后[[细胞核|核]]内[[染色质|染色质]]不可逆的压缩。接着会发生[[核破裂|核破裂]]。[[红血球|红血球]]或[[中性白血球|中性白血球]]成熟时也会观察到固缩。

